			</ul>
			<ul class="nav navbar-nav navbar-right">
				<li class="dropdown"><a href="#" class="dropdown-toggle" data-toggle="dropdown" role="button" aria-haspopup="true" aria-expanded="false">회원정보<span
						class="caret"></span></a>
